com.sun.tools.visualvm.application

Class Application

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sun.tools.visualvm.core.datasource.DataSource
      • com.sun.tools.visualvm.application.Application
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Stateful

    public abstract class Application
extends DataSource
implements Stateful
    Abstract implementation of Application. Each application is defined by a Host on which it's running and an unique identificator.

    Jiri Sedlacek
